<DIV>All totally in class character for a fighter that makes himself the target of all attacks and uses weapons to damage his foes. That's what a tank is and all of those abilities are in class charater for a Tank. A TANK doesn't set up a field hospital - that's a Cleric sir.&nbsp;Doing damage at range was a sufficient reason for&nbsp;Rangers to no longer be able to tank, but at least that's an understandable skill for a FIGHTER to have. Ressing and Buffing are not - fighters don't do that, Clerics do and ya do it virtually inditinguishably from Clerics.</DIV>
