		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>"When you balance out a class, your not looking at just three classes, there are several class's in the game that are directly effected, not just the Knights, when you start adding utilities to Warriors."</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I don't know how much more clear I can make it.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Knights campaigned for an avoidance/mitigation ability and got one.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>They campaigned to have their survivability gap with Warriors NARROWED and got it in an epic with effects that assist in their survivability, a return on AC past the softcap "very close" to Warriors, adjustments to spells including higher level stuns, etc.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>And SoE was so pleased with this that they posted that their <U>goal</U> of having Knights tank all single-group content interchangably with Warriors had been largely met.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Futher, that Defensive is not needed to succeed vs any single-group content.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Providing MORE HP's or AC to Warriors given the direction chosen by SoE is totally and completely immaterial.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>We have what is fundamentally Three Equal Tanks in all single-group content Two With Spellbooks.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The Three Equal Tanks part of this is NOT going to change. No elevation of of Warriro AC, HP's or mitigation is going to be allowed to change it.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>What Warriors desperately need is to narrow the advantages granted to 2 out of the 3 classes that tank beyond ours.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>"there are several class's in the game that are directly effected, not just the Knights, when you start adding utilities to Warriors."</DIV>
<DIV>OMGoodness!!</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Don't you think several classes in the game&nbsp;are affected by the fact Paladins can Tank AND 90% Res, provide Clerical buffs, spot heal, GRC, etc???</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Adding abilities to Warriors that other classes that tank already have isn't going to effect the game any more than the fact that Paladins and SK's already have these out of Tank Archetype abilities.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I hate to sya this, but you sound exactly like a mid-level player hoping for an ill-advised and unneed upgrade to tanking abilities cause you feel that you can not compete given what you have earned by in game accomplishent.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Three Equal Tanks in single group content is here guy, get used to it.</DIV><p>Message Edited by Battleblade-Xegony on <span class=date_text>06-27-2005</span> <span class=time_text>02:11 PM</span>	
		</td></tr>
